title: Xp Sp3 RTM 5512
description:
Windows Xp Service Pack 3 RTM 5512

Dedicated to my dearest friends in Spain.

Much more respect, ... this version has s-ata drivers included for toshiba laptops
and some performance settings .

I used Windows Xp Service pack 0 as source and Sp3 MSDN version as Sp,.. slipstreamed.

It is fully genuine , no serial needed to install, no crack for activation....  Enjoy!

Best of Wishes!
